Package: survatr
Title: Causal Survival Analysis for Methodological Triangulation
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Date: 2026-04-22
Authors@R: 
    person("Lorenzo", "Fabbri", , "lorenzo.fabbri92sm@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3031-322X"))
Description: Causal survival analysis via pooled-logistic hazard
    g-computation, inverse probability weighting, and iterated conditional
    expectation (ICE) on person-period data. Extends the causatr engine to
    time-to-event outcomes with delta-method sandwich variance on
    cumulative-product survival curves, risk difference / risk ratio /
    RMST contrasts, competing-risks cause-specific hazards, and empirical
    bootstrap. Part of the etverse ecosystem.
